% V. EXPERIMENTS
% ==============================================================================
\section{Experiments}\label{sec:experiments}

\emph{Platform.}
KUKA IIWA14 7-DOF ($D{=}7$), Ubuntu~22.04, Intel Core~i7.
All GCS-based methods use the Drake~\cite{tedrake2019drake} SOCP solver
with Mosek~\cite{mosek2024} as the backend.
SBF is implemented in Python/Cython; collision queries use AABB--AABB
tests against obstacle bounding boxes.

\emph{Scenes.}
Three environments of increasing difficulty (\cref{tab:scenes}).

