Dense-20    & 20 & Narrow passages \\
\bottomrule
\end{tabular}
\end{table}

\emph{Baselines.}
\Cref{tab:baselines} lists the methods compared.
SBF and C-IRIS both feed into the same GCS-SOCP solver for fair
comparison of region quality.
Both methods provide certified collision-free regions, enabling
a controlled evaluation of region-generation efficiency and
downstream planning performance.

